{"lemma":"رَحَى","slug":"رَحَى","root":"ر.ح.#","root_slug":"ر-ح-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ح-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n15103"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%89"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"millstone"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make a turn"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to coil, to twist"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ra.ħaː/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n15103","headword_ar":"رَحًى","root":"rHw and rHY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, &c.) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHFA","text_ar":"رَحًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, * K,) the former of which is the more approved, (TA,) and some say ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaA='N","text_ar":"رَحَا=ءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mill;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAHuwnN","text_ar":"طَاحُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) [and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mill-stone;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"great round stone with which one grinds:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) of the fem. gender: (Zj, S, Msb, K:) dual of the first"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHayaAni","text_ar":"رَحَيَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) and of the second"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHawaAni","text_ar":"رَحَوَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, * K,) and of the third,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaAA=ni","text_ar":"رَحَاا=نِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) the pl. (of pauc., S) of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHFY","text_ar":"رَحًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) [and of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHFA","text_ar":"رَحًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroHK","text_ar":"اَرْحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (of mult., S)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroHaA='N","text_ar":"اَرْحَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) which latter is the pl. that is preferred accord. to IAmb, (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruHiY~N","text_ar":"رُحِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riHiY~N","text_ar":"رِحِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K, TA,) with damm and with kesr (Msb, TA) to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) [for the last of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHiY~N","text_ar":"رَحِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is substituted in the CK,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uroHiY~N","text_ar":"اُرْحِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) with damm, and with kesr to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"H","text_ar":"ح"},{"kind":"text","text":"and teshdeed to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) [in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroHiY~N","text_ar":"اَرْحِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroHiyapN","text_ar":"اَرْحِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) which is extr., (K,) said by AHát to be wrong, and by IAmb to be anomalous, and by Zj to be not allowable, (Msb,) in the T said to be as though it were a pl. pl., (TA,) or it is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaA='N","text_ar":"رَحَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and therefore regular]: (S:) the dim. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruHay~apN","text_ar":"رُحَيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Zj, Msb.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaA Alyadi","text_ar":"رَحَا اليَدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaY Alyadi","text_ar":"رَحَى اليَدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The hand-mill."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A molar tooth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grinder:"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DirosN","text_ar":"ضِرْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Msb, K;) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroHaA='N","text_ar":"اَرْحَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aDoraAsN","text_ar":"اَضْرَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) [or rather] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroHaA='","text_ar":"اَرْحَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", also called the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TawaAHin","text_ar":"طَوَاحِن"},{"kind":"text","text":", are the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twelve teeth, three on each side"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"above and below"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"next after the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DawaAHik","text_ar":"ضَوَاحِك"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bicuspids"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Zj, in his “ Khalk el-Insán. ”) ―         -b3-  [And app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A roller with which land is rolled to crush the clods;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as being likened to a mill-stone: see 1 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xtm","text_ar":"ختم"},{"kind":"text","text":", near the end of the paragraph.] ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Stones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a great rock,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mass of stone."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A round piece of ground, rising above what surrounds it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"about as large in extent as a mile:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroHaA='N","text_ar":"اَرْحَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) or this latter, i. e. the pl., signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieces of rugged ground, less than mountains, round, and rising above what surrounds them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHFA","text_ar":"رَحًا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"مِنَ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a round and rugged place"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among sands:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a large and rugged"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevation such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaArap","text_ar":"قَارَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akamap","text_ar":"اَكَمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"round, rising above what surrounds it, not spreading upon the surface of the earth, nor producing herbs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leguminous plants, nor trees."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh, TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A round cloud;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as being likened to a mill-stone;] (A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rjH","text_ar":"رجح"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaY saHaAbK","text_ar":"رَحَى سَحَابٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b7-  The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kirokirap","text_ar":"كِرْكِرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"callous protuberance upon the breast"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of a camel; (T, S, K;) so called because of its roundness: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroHaA='N","text_ar":"اَرْحَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) which likewise signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"callous protuberances upon the knees"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the camel. (T, TA.) ―         -b8-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foot"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firosin","text_ar":"فِرْسِن"},{"kind":"text","text":") of the camel and of the elephant: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroHaA='N","text_ar":"اَرْحَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAy^irap","text_ar":"دَايِرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"circling border"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"around the nail."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b10-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"breast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chest:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl., as in the other senses following,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroHaA='N","text_ar":"اَرْحَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b11-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Spinage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spinach;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) because of the roundness of its leaves. (TA.) ―         -b12-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A collective body of the members of a household."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, K, TA.) ―         -b13-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An independent tribe:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroHaA='N","text_ar":"اَرْحَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(which is its pl., K, TA) signifies (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"independent tribes, that are in no need of others."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) ―         -b14-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A large number"},{"kind":"text","text":"of camels,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crowding,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pressing, together;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;) also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaH~aAnapN","text_ar":"طَحَّانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaA AlA_ibili","text_ar":"رَحَا الاـِبِلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the collective herd of the camels:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaA Alqawomi","text_ar":"رَحَا القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the collective body of the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, TA.) ―         -b15-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaY Alqawomi","text_ar":"رَحَى القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies [also] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The chief of the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, K, TA.) [It is added in the TA that 'Omar Ibn-El-Khattáb was called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaY AlHarobi","text_ar":"رَحَى الحَرْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as though meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The chief of war;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of his warlike propensities: but it seems from what here follows, as well as from what precedes, that this may be a mistranscription, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaY Alqawomi","text_ar":"رَحَى القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaY AlEarabi","text_ar":"رَحَى العَرَبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b16-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaY AlHarobi","text_ar":"رَحَى الحَرْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The most vehement part"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thickest"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the fight;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawomatuhaA","text_ar":"حَوْمَتُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb:) in the K it is said that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~aHaY","text_ar":"الرَّحَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hawomapu AlHarobi","text_ar":"حَوْمَةُ الحَرْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEoZamuhu","text_ar":"مُعْظَمُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaroHaY","text_ar":"المَرْحَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": but it seems that there is an omission;"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1058},{"kind":"text","text":"for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHrb","text_ar":"الحرب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is [generally] fem., and in the M it is said that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaY Almawoti","text_ar":"رَحَى المَوْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEoZamuhu","text_ar":"مُعْظَمُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the main stress,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thickest, of death"},{"kind":"text","text":"in battle]. (TA.) In a saying relating to 'Alee's having made an end of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljamali","text_ar":"الجَمَلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maroHay","text_ar":"مَرْحَي","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", this expression is expl. by A 'Obeyd as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The place around which revolved the thickest of the fight"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmawoDiEu Al~a*iy daArato Ealayohi raHay AlHarobi","text_ar":"المَوْضِعُ الَّذِي دَارَتْ عَلَيْهِ رَحَي الحَرْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":") [in the Battle"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the Camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daArato Ealayohi","text_ar":"دَارَتْ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHay Almawoti","text_ar":"رَحَي المَوْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which may be rendered (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The main stress of death beset him round about"},{"kind":"text","text":"] means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"death befell him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","Msb","Zj","K","M","Sh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}